Translates Daredevil Noir #1-4.

Betty and Veronica are on their way to a party held by Riverdale's reigning fashion queen Sheila Wu-and Veronica's determined to out-dress her at her own party! However, on their way to the gala, Betty encounters a young girl with some animal friends in need of assistance on the side of the road. The adventure begins as Betty, Veronica, and their new acquaintance Alina try to wrangle up her stray pets. Will the pets be safely returned? Will Betty and Veronica make it to the party unscathed? Find out in "The Perils of Pet Sitting," the exciting lead story to this jumbo-sized comics digest!
